                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                    <div id="about" class="tabcontent">
                        <h1 class="font-weight-bold mb-4">Beachfront Bliss: Best India Hotels with Spa & Sea Views | Book My Hotels</h1>

                        <!-- Intro -->
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm mb-4">
                            <p>
                                There’s something magical about waking up to the sound of waves, watching golden sunsets over the sea, and indulging in a soothing spa session overlooking the ocean. Whether you’re planning a romantic retreat, a relaxing solo escape, or a luxurious family holiday, India’s coastline is dotted with beautiful beachfront hotels offering world-class spas and breathtaking sea views.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                At <strong>Book My Hotels</strong>, we’ve handpicked the best beachfront hotels in India with spa and sea views, where luxury meets serenity — and every stay feels like a dream come true.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 1 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">1. The Leela Kovalam, Kerala</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Perched dramatically on a cliff overlooking the Arabian Sea, The Leela Kovalam is South Asia’s only cliff-top beach resort. With private cottages, infinity pools, and an award-winning spa, it’s the perfect place to relax and rejuvenate.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    The hotel’s Ayurvedic spa therapies and ocean-view dining experiences make it one of the best beachfront resorts in India for couples and wellness seekers.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Spa lovers, luxury travelers, and honeymooners.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 2 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">2. Taj Exotica Resort & Spa, Goa</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Located on the tranquil Benaulim Beach, Taj Exotica Goa is a tropical paradise spread across lush gardens. The Jiva Spa offers holistic Indian wellness therapies with sea-facing treatment rooms — a perfect combination of luxury and tranquility.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    The resort’s Portuguese-style villas and private plunge pools create an unmatched romantic beach escape in India.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Couples and families seeking a relaxing Goan holiday.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 3 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">3. The Oberoi Beach Resort, Baliapanda, Puri</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Overlooking the Bay of Bengal, The Oberoi Beach Resort blends timeless elegance with seaside charm. Its spa offers rejuvenating massages inspired by traditional Indian therapies, and the rooms come with spectacular sea views.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    The serene ambiance makes it one of the best spa resorts on India’s east coast.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Peaceful getaways and luxury spa experiences.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 4 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">4. Marari Beach Resort, Alappuzha</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    For those seeking eco-luxury, Marari Beach Resort in Kerala offers a blend of rustic charm and comfort. Thatched villas, organic cuisine, yoga sessions, and Ayurvedic treatments by the sea create a holistic retreat that reconnects you with nature.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Wellness travelers and couples seeking eco-friendly stays.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 5 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">5. Radisson Blu Resort & Spa, Mahabalipuram</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    This beachside resort combines heritage and modern luxury on the scenic Coromandel Coast. With elegant sea-facing rooms and a full-service spa offering rejuvenation packages, it’s a favorite among couples and families alike.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    You can explore the nearby UNESCO temple complex and unwind by the infinity pool — all in one stay.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Best for:</strong> Weekend getaways and family beach vacations.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Closing Section -->
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm mt-5">
                            <h4 class="mb-3">Experience Coastal Luxury with Book My Hotels</h4>
                            <p>
                                At Book My Hotels, we make it easy for you to find and book India’s best beachfront hotels with spa and sea views. Whether you crave the wellness vibes of Kerala, the festive charm of Goa, or the peace of the Andaman Islands, our curated listings ensure comfort, beauty, and unforgettable experiences.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                So go ahead — unwind by the sea, pamper yourself with a spa session, and experience the true meaning of beachfront bliss.
                            </p>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
